Original Verilog code is as follows: 
```verilog






































module Audio_Clock 
(
	input areset,
	input inclk0,
	output c0,
	output locked
);

reg  	[10:0] COUNTER_500;
wire  CLOCK_500 = COUNTER_500[9];
assign c0 = COUNTER_500[1];

always @(posedge inclk0)
	COUNTER_500 <= COUNTER_500 + 1;

endmodule













































































































































































































































































```

